title: James Newton Howard & Friends
description:
The album James Newton Howard & friends features Jeff Porcaro, Mike Porcaro, Joe Porcaro & David Paich. The album was recorded at the now legendary Sheffield Lab using Direct To Disc laquering.
The music on it was used to Promote the release of the Yamaha DX-7 at NAMM.
A must for AOR/Toto fans.

Features song like E minor Shuffle and gone buttlefishing.

Excellent drumming by Jeff & Joe Porcaro
